@startuml
title GB Studio - System Context

actor "Creator" as User
rectangle "GB Studio App" as App
database "Project Files" as Project
rectangle "Build Toolchain" as Toolchain
rectangle "External Editors" as Editors

User --> App : Create/Open/Edit Project
App --> Project : Read/Write Assets + Project Data
App --> Toolchain : Compile/Export
App --> Editors : Open files with configured tools
Toolchain --> Project : Output Build Artifacts

@enduml
